name: Cancelled Maze Game Prototype
description:
!!!READ BEFORE PLAYING!!!

this was a prototype for a maze horror game i was going to make called "The House", unfortunately it fell through due to working on other projects.

Even though there are no enemies in this build of the game i think the 2 levels currently available will be fun to explore while trying to find all of the pickups

to get to Level 2 you will need to collect all 6 of the "pages" which are untextured floating spheres

CONTROLS

WASD - movement

E - Pickup

F - Flashlight

SPACE - Jump
